    m_Alignment: 0
    m_AlignByGeometry: 0
    m_RichText: 0
    m_HorizontalOverflow: 0
    m_VerticalOverflow: 1
    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: "\u2022 Di chuy\u1EC3n: d\xF9ng ph\xEDm ho\u1EB7c \u0111i\u1EC1u khi\u1EC3n
    theo thi\u1EBFt l\u1EADp trong game (WASD / m\u0169i t\xEAn t\xF9y b\u1EA3n build).\n\u2022
    T\u01B0\u01A1ng t\xE1c: \u0111\u1EBFn g\u1EA7n \u0111i\u1EC3m g\u1EE3i \xFD /
    NPC / v\u1EADt th\u1EC3 v\xE0 d\xF9ng ph\xEDm t\u01B0\u01A1ng t\xE1c khi c\xF3
    nh\u1EAFc tr\xEAn m\xE0n h\xECnh.\n\u2022 Nhi\u1EC7m v\u1EE5: m\u1EDF nh\u1EADt
    k\xFD / m\u1EE5c ti\xEAu (n\u1EBFu c\xF3 trong scene) \u0111\u1EC3 bi\u1EBFt
    vi\u1EC7c c\u1EA7n l\xE0m ti\u1EBFp theo.\n\u2022 L\u01B0u: tu\u1EF3 c\u1EA5u
    h\xECnh project \u2014 tho\xE1t qua menu ho\u1EB7c checkpoint t\u1EF1 \u0111\u1ED9ng.\n\nT\u1EEB
    menu ch\xEDnh: Ch\u01A1i \u2014 b\u1EAFt \u0111\u1EA7u (c\u1EA7n th\xEAm scene
    gameplay v\xE0o Build Settings sau MainMenu); Tho\xE1t \u2014 \u0111\xF3ng game."
